snippet.title: Aquaman Movie Review | Jason Momoa | Amber Heard | Spoiler-Free Honest Review
snippet.description:
Arthur Curry (Jason Momoa) is born to lighthouse keeper and the Queen of Atlantis, Atlantana (Nicole Kidman). He can breathe under water and on the surface.

Amber Heard (Princess Mera) want him to come back to Atlantis and reclaim his throne from King Orm (Patrick Wilson). 

Cast: Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, patrick Wilson, Nicole Kidman, Yahya Abdul-Mateen II, Willem Dofoe.

Director: James Wan
